ministration and a Fellow of the Institute of Policy and Management Development.  He is also an awardee of the prestigious Nigerian Humanitarian Icon Award (NIHIA), the African International Achievers Award (Ghana) and the Life Ambassador of Peace in Africa Award (Ghana), all bestowed on him in 2018.\n\nThe Acting Polytechnic Librarian, Dr. Ademola Fijabi is a distinguished author and an academic of repute with several articles published in reputable national and international journals.  His immeasurable contributions to national development of Libraries in Nigeria cannot be over-emphasized.  He has served on several important committees in Yaba College of Technology both as Chairman and member.  \n\nHis academic prowess and professional dexterity has adequately been recognized by front-line institutions within and outside the shores of Nigeria.\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '07-17', '1');
