ers (SWE)', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'i.    Renewable Energy in Photovoltaic Technology\r\nii.   Renewable Energy in Concentrated Solar Energy (CSP) Technology\r\niii.  Renewable Energy in Solar Tower Power Technology\r\niv.  Energy efficiency Improvement\r\nv.   Sustainable Green Building Technology\r\nvi.  Building Information Modeling (BIM) (Architecture)\r\nvii. Building Integrated Renewable Energy, and CO2 emissions \r\nviii. Hybrid Solar Power Plants, GAS TURBINE\r\nix.  Economic Analysis of Power Production\r\nx.   Energy based Analysis in Thermal Systems\r\nxi.  Electrical Power System Technology', 'A.  LIST OF SEMINARS ATTENDED\r\n\r\ni.	Competitive Power College (CPC 105) – Renewable Energy Venture Development, (2012). Organised by Renewable Energy World Conference & Expo, Held at Orange County Convention Center, Orlando Florida, U.S.A.\r\n\r\nii.	The Application of Remote Sensing and Geographic Information System in Research and National Development, (2012). Organised by the Environmental Research Group, Yaba Tech, in conjunction with National Space Research and Development Agency. \r\n         Held at Yaba College of Technology.\r\n\r\niii.	Use of Information and Communication Technology (ICT) For Teaching and Research (2011). Organized by Science and Technology Education Post Basic (STEP-B) Project, Held at Yaba College of Technology, Lagos Nigeria.\r\n\r\niv.	Project Development and Management/Professional Research Skills (2011). Held at the Centre For Applied Research and Technology Innovation, Yaba College of Technology, Lagos Nigeria.\r\n\r\nv.	ICT for Proposal Writing and Analysis (2010). Held at the School of Engineering, Yaba College of Technology, Lagos Nigeria.\r\n\r\nvi.	Grant-oriented Proposals and Conducting Research (2009). Held at The School of Engineering, Yaba College Of Technology.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nB.    LIST OF CONFERENCES ATTENDED\r\n\r\ni.	Southern African Universities Power Engineering Conference/Robotics and Mechatronics/Pattern Recognition