ign Affairs, Israelis Agency for International Development\nCooperation) International R&D Course on Food Security & Grain Storage- Technologies\nand Management in Collaboration with Ministry of agriculture and Rural Development.\nTraining sponsored by Israeli government, from 2-17th December 2013.\n\n8. Advanced Digital Appreciation Programme for Tertiary Institutions course, organized and\nheld at Digital Bridge Institute, Cappa, Oshodi, Nigeria in collaboration with International\nCentre for Communication Studies in collaboration with National Communication\nCommission from 15th\n– 189th July 2103\n\n9. In-House Training of Trainers Workshop on Research Instrument Design, Administration\nand Data Analysis Using Statistical Package for Social Sciences (SPSS) organized by\nCentre for Applied Research and Technology Innovation at ICT Computer Training centre,\nYaba College of Technology on the 17 & 18th of September 2013.\n\n10. In-House Training of Trainers Workshop on Grant –Oriented Proposals and Conducting\nResearch by Centre for Applied Research and Technology Innovation at ICT Computer\nTraining centre, Yaba College of Technology on the 22nd\n- 24th April 2008. \n3\n\nADMINISTRATIVE EXPERIENCE AND RESPONSIBILITIES\nHead, Dept. of Food Tech., Yaba College of Tech. March. 2019 - Till Date\nStudents Industrial Work Experience Scheme (SIWES)\nCoordinator, Yaba College of Technology March. 2018 – March 2019\nMember, School of Technology, Yaba College of Technology\nCommittee on Staff Promotion Sept. 2019- Till Date Member,\nStudents Disciplinary Committee, Yaba College of Technology\nClass Manager ND 1 Food Technology Jan.2015 - Dec. 2017\nMember, National Board for Technical Education (NBTE)\nre - accreditation committee Jan. 2016 - Till Date\nAssistant General Secretary ASUP (Yabatech Chapter) Dec. 2006 - Dec. 2008\nExamination officer (Food Technology Department) Feb. 2005 - Dec. 2006\n\nWORK EXPERIENCE\n1. Yaba College of Technology, Department of Food Technolo